Seven out of 10 FTSE 100 bosses think Ed Miliband would be a 'catastrophe' for Britain if he wins the election . 
  More than 100 company bosses have signed a letter warning against a Labour government . 
  Poll of 35 chairman backs David Cameron to remain Prime Minister . 
  Comes after Miliband pledged to hold in-out referendum on Europe . 
  Boots chief executive Stefano Pessina said it would be 'a catastrophe'